title: Pixel don't call in Estonian network
content:
Hi!

I've to buy my Google Pixel XL 1 in Russia, but where it was buying firstly I don't know. In Russia pixel is worked correctly I can call, use the network, etc. But when I've arrived in Estonia my phone write "Calls not allowed", when I use Estonian sim. I've tried to factory reset, reboot, change the sim card, nothing. Sim card is work correct. Maybe, somebody can help me?
